00:08:11.470 --> 00:08:17.470
They will do no harm nor cause any ruin in all my holy mountain says Jehovah.

00:08:17.470 --> 00:08:25.199
Skilled artists in the art department at world headquarters beautifully illustrate such scenes

00:08:25.199 --> 00:08:28.199
