00:08:32.200 --> 00:08:35.200
This will be real.

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:41.200
Think how you'll feel when you're not afraid of wild animals and the animals aren't afraid of you.

00:08:41.200 --> 00:08:50.610
As we look forward to that future promise of peace, what can we do now to pursue peace?

00:08:50.610 --> 00:09:01.610
One thing is to contribute to the peace of our spiritual paradise, the secure, spiritually prosperous environment in which we worship Jehovah.

00:09:01.610 --> 00:09:08.610
Jesus stated at Matthew chapter 5 verse 9, happy are the peacemakers.

00:09:08.610 --> 00:09:13.610
A peacemaker is skilled at restoring peace among brothers when peace is disturbed.

00:09:13.610 --> 00:09:20.610
But more importantly, a peacemaker strives to avoid disturbing peace in the first place.

00:09:20.610 --> 00:09:23.610
Does peacemaker describe you?

00:09:23.610 --> 00:09:27.610
Are you contributing to our spiritual paradise in that way?

00:09:27.610 --> 00:09:35.269
Something else we can do as we await the future fulfillment of the wolf and the lamb feeding together

00:09:35.269 --> 00:09:43.269
is to meditate on what it will be like to help resurrected ones who were violent to become peaceable.

00:09:43.269 --> 00:09:52.269
Imagine studying with a resurrected one who had a violent background, perhaps experiencing a violent death because of a fierce personality.

00:09:52.269 --> 00:09:59.269
